 two warships to Coast Guard| publisher=[[The Independent (Bangladesh newspaper)|The Independent]]| date=4 August 2016| accessdate=4 November 2016| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161104205734/http://www.theindependentbd.com/post/54360#| archive-date=2016-11-04| url-status=live}}</ref> Two ships arrived in [[Port of Chittagong|Chittagong]] on 2 November 2016.<ref>{{cite web| url=http://www.janes.com/article/65289/new-opv-deliveries-see-bangladesh-s-coastguard-continue-to-expand| title=New OPV deliveries see Bangladesh's coastguard continue to expand| publisher=[[IHS Jane's]]| date=4 November 2016| accessdate=4 November 2016| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161105033015/http://www.janes.com/article/65289/new-opv-deliveries-see-bangladesh-s-coastguard-continue-to-expand#| archive-date=2016-11-05| url-status=live}}</ref>\n|-\n! colspan=\"7\" style=\"background: lavender;\"| Sea trial (2)\n|-\n|[[Minerva-class corvette#Leader Class OPV|Leader Class OPV]]||[[File:Coast Guard Ship (Bangladesh).jpg|200px]]|| [[Patrol boat#Classification|Offshore Patrol Vessel]] || [[CGS Mansoor Ali]] (PL 73) <br> [[CGS Kamaruzzaman]] (PL 74)  || {{ITA}} || {{align|center|1 285}} || ''Urania'' and ''Danaide'' were delivered after refitting on 12 October 2017<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.defnat.com/e-RDN/vue-tribune.php?ctribune=1031 |title=Une nouvelle vie pour deux anciennes corvettes italiennes, un exemple \u00e0 suivre |date=11 November 2017 |website=Revue D\u00e9fense nationale |language=fr }}</ref> and arrived in [[Port of Mongla|Mongla]] on 22 December 2017.<ref>{{cite web| url=http://www.thedailystar.net/city/2-patrol-vessels-join-coast-guard-fleet-today-1508605| title=2 patrol vessels join Coast Guard fleet| publisher=[[The Daily Star (Bangladesh)|The Daily Star]]| date=22 December 2017| accessdate=23 December 2017| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171223172551/http://www.thedailystar.net/city/2-patrol-vessels-join-coast-guard-fleet-today-1508605#| ar