e=JA/><ref name=AC/><ref name=DL/><ref name=NJ/><ref name=FI/>\n* [[Cessna Citation Sovereign]]<ref name=AP/><ref name=JA/><ref name=AC/>\n* [[Cessna Citation X]]<ref name=AP/><ref name=JA/><ref name=AC/><ref name=DL/><ref name=NJ/><ref name=FI/>\n* [[Dassault Falcon 50]]<ref name=JA/><ref name=AC/><ref name=DL/><ref name=FI/>\n* [[Gulfstream G200]]/G250<ref name=AP/><ref name=JA/><ref name=AC/><ref name=NJ/><ref name=FMsmsj/><ref name=FI/>\n* [[Hawker 4000]]<ref name=JA/><ref name=FMsmsj/><ref name=FI>{{cite web |url= https://www.flightglobal.com/assets/getAsset.aspx?ItemID=14999 |title= Super Mid-Size Jets |work= Flight International }}</ref>\nThey typically accommodate 10\u201311 passengers over a {{#expr:(3063+3125+4018+3646+3250)/5round0}} nmi average range, with a ${{#expr:(18.79+19.995+20.995+24.5+26.673)/5round1}}M mean price:\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|+ Super mid-size jets, 4 pax mission<ref name=PPH2019/>\n|-\n! Model !! Pax !! Length !! Span !! int. L !! int. W\n! Engines !! Thrust !! MTOW !! Range !! Cruise !! Fuel/nm\n|-\n| [[Citation Sovereign]]+ <!--$17.9M-->\t|| 9\u201312\t|| 63.5&nbsp;ft\t|| 72.3&nbsp;ft\t|| 25.3&nbsp;ft\t|| 5.7&nbsp;ft\t|| 2 [[Pratt & Whitney Canada PW300|PW300]]\t|| {{#expr:2*5907}} lbf\t|| 30,775&nbsp;lb\t|| 3,069&nbsp;nmi\t|| 402 kn\t|| {{#expr:9679/3069round2}} lb\t\n|-\n| [[Embraer Legacy 500|Legacy 500]] <!--$20M-->\t|| 8\u201312\t|| 68.1&nbsp;ft\t|| 66.4&nbsp;ft\t|| 24.6&nbsp;ft\t|| 6.8&nbsp;ft\t|| 2 [[Honeywell HTF7000|HTF7000]]\t|| {{#expr:2*7036}} lbf\t|| 38,360&nbsp;lb\t|| 3,125&nbsp;nmi\t|| 433 kn\t|| {{#expr:11222/3125round2}} lb\n|-\n| [[Embraer Legacy 500|Praetor 600]] <!--$20.995M-->\t|| 8\u201312\t|| 68.1&nbsp;ft\t|| 66.4&nbsp;ft\t|| 24.6&nbsp;ft\t|| 6.8&nbsp;ft\t|| 2 [[Honeywell HTF7000|HTF7000]]\t|| {{#expr:2*7528}} lbf\t|| 42,857&nbsp;lb\t|| 4,018&nbsp;nmi\t|| 423 kn\t|| {{#expr:14404/4018round2}} lb\n|-\n| [[Gulfstream G280]] <!--$24.5M-->\t|| 10\u201319\t|| 66.8&nbsp;ft\t|| 63.0&nbsp;ft\t|| 25.8&nbs