ax mission<ref name=PPH2019/>\n|-\n! Model !! Pax !! Length !! Span !! int. L !! int. W\n! Engines !! Thrust !! MTOW !! Range !! Cruise !! Fuel/nm\n|-\n| [[Citation Sovereign]]+ <!--$17.9M-->\t|| 9\u201312\t|| 63.5&nbsp;ft\t|| 72.3&nbsp;ft\t|| 25.3&nbsp;ft\t|| 5.7&nbsp;ft\t|| 2 [[Pratt & Whitney Canada PW300|PW300]]\t|| {{#expr:2*5907}} lbf\t|| 30,775&nbsp;lb\t|| 3,069&nbsp;nmi\t|| 402 kn\t|| {{#expr:9679/3069round2}} lb\t\n|-\n| [[Embraer Legacy 500|Legacy 500]] <!--$20M-->\t|| 8\u201312\t|| 68.1&nbsp;ft\t|| 66.4&nbsp;ft\t|| 24.6&nbsp;ft\t|| 6.8&nbsp;ft\t|| 2 [[Honeywell HTF7000|HTF7000]]\t|| {{#expr:2*7036}} lbf\t|| 38,360&nbsp;lb\t|| 3,125&nbsp;nmi\t|| 433 kn\t|| {{#expr:11222/3125round2}} lb\n|-\n| [[Embraer Legacy 500|Praetor 600]] <!--$20.995M-->\t|| 8\u201312\t|| 68.1&nbsp;ft\t|| 66.4&nbsp;ft\t|| 24.6&nbsp;ft\t|| 6.8&nbsp;ft\t|| 2 [[Honeywell HTF7000|HTF7000]]\t|| {{#expr:2*7528}} lbf\t|| 42,857&nbsp;lb\t|| 4,018&nbsp;nmi\t|| 423 kn\t|| {{#expr:14404/4018round2}} lb\n|-\n| [[Gulfstream G280]] <!--$24.5M-->\t|| 10\u201319\t|| 66.8&nbsp;ft\t|| 63.0&nbsp;ft\t|| 25.8&nbsp;ft\t|| 7.2&nbsp;ft\t|| 2 [[Honeywell HTF7000|HTF7000]]\t|| {{#expr:2*7624}} lbf\t|| 39,600&nbsp;lb\t|| 3,646&nbsp;nmi\t|| 451 kn\t|| {{#expr:12761/3646round2}} lb\n|-\n| [[Bombardier Challenger 300|Challenger 350]] <!--$26.7M-->\t|| 9-11\t|| 68.7&nbsp;ft\t|| 69.0&nbsp;ft\t|| 25.2&nbsp;ft\t|| 7.2&nbsp;ft\t|| 2 [[Honeywell HTF7000|HTF7000]]\t|| {{#expr:2*7323}} lbf\t|| 40,600&nbsp;lb\t|| 3,250&nbsp;nmi\t|| 448 kn\t|| {{#expr:12212/3250round2}} lb\n|}\n\n===Large jets===\n\n[[File:EM N601GT (2935602297).jpg|thumb|More than 1000 [[Challenger 600]] have been produced.]]\n\n* [[Bombardier Challenger 600]]<ref name=AP/><ref name=JA/><ref name=BAP/>\n* [[Dassault Falcon 2000]](ER)<ref name=AP/><ref name=JA/><ref name=BAP/>\n* [[Dassault Falcon 900]]<ref name=JA/><ref name=AC/><ref name=DL/><ref name=BAP/>\n* [[Embraer Legacy 600]]/650<ref name=AP/><ref name=JA/><ref name=BAP/>\n\nThey typically accommod